title: Miami Dolphins blow out Houston Texans, claw back to .500
text:
Miami Dolphins blow out Houston Texans, claw back to .500 
Ryan Tannehill sets an NFL record with 25 straight completions 
Lamar Miller has two touchdowns of over 50 yards 
Jarvis Landry also scores twice for resurgent Dolphins Miami Dolphins Lamar Miller 26, celebrates with Rishard Matthews 18, and Jarvis Landry 14, after Miller scored a second quarter touchdown as they play the Houston Texans at Sun Life Stadium in Miami Gardens, Florida, October 25, 2015.
